{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1059220/extras/1983-intro.gif?t=1738371824\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's 1983. The tensions between NATO and the USSR have reached their breaking point, and the Cold War has quickly turned into an all-out conflict across Europe. Take the side of NATO or Warsaw Pact forces in an authentic, realistic, yet accessible online first person tactical shooter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to '83!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Born in the house of the Rising Storm</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">'83 is a spiritual successor to the Rising Storm 2 series - and it's not just the accessible realism approach that makes us that. Members of our team helped shape all previous Rising Storm games, as well as Red Orchestra games. This is what we do, and this is what we do best.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Squad based. Objective oriented. Fast time to action.<br>Classic gameplay you're all familiar with - but in Unreal Engine 5.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The practical gameplay of '83 stands on several pillars - the two most prominent ones are your squad, and your objective. One is a key to the other: without well organized squads, capturing or defending objectives becomes challenging.\u00a0</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1059220/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738371824","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1059220/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738371824","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1059220/53048ea14c43ad140e80e5724187bc1479d71b7a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738371824","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1059220/53048ea14c43ad140e80e5724187bc1479d71b7a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738371824","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Includes level editor","id":17},{"description":"Includes Source SDK","id":16}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"There will be blood and moderate gory imagery in '83, reflective of wounds received in real-life military combat. This will occur when players receive damage from explosions or incendiary devices."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1059220/extras/1983-intro.gif?t=1738371824\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's 1983. The tensions between NATO and the USSR have reached their breaking point, and the Cold War has quickly turned into an all-out conflict across Europe. Take the side of NATO or Warsaw Pact forces in an authentic, realistic, yet accessible online first person tactical shooter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to '83!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Born in the house of the Rising Storm</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">'83 is a spiritual successor to the Rising Storm 2 series - and it's not just the accessible realism approach that makes us that. Members of our team helped shape all previous Rising Storm games, as well as Red Orchestra games. This is what we do, and this is what we do best.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Squad based. Objective oriented. Fast time to action.<br>Classic gameplay you're all familiar with - but in Unreal Engine 5.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The practical gameplay of '83 stands on several pillars - the two most prominent ones are your squad, and your objective. One is a key to the other: without well organized squads, capturing or defending objectives becomes challenging.\u00a0</p>","developers":["Blue Dot Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Massively Multiplayer","id":"29"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":